Changelog for Roleman
----------------------

2017-10-19  0.3.0
            Added role-level settings/guc functions
            Added ability to set max connections
            Added ability to set per-role search paths

2017-09-29  0.2.1
            Added missing missing files for 0.2.x
            Tests now test against SQL object injection
            Added upgrade tests.

2017-09-29  0.2.0
            Added roleman.alter_base(rolename, attrs)
            Tests now properly pass on 9.4 and higher
            Some documentation improvements

2017-09-27  0.1.1
            Documentation and manifest improvements

2017-09-26  0.1
            First Version Released to the World

